name: Egg    Jalapeño Cheese Appetizer
ingredients: 7 ounce can sliced pickled jalapeños, drained and chopped (about 3/4 cup)
8 ounces cheddar or colby cheese, shredded

instructions.en: Whisk the eggs well in a mixing bowl
instructions.ja: ボウルで卵をよく泡立てる

instructions.en: Drain and chop the pickled jalapeños
instructions.ja: ピクルスのハラペーニョの水気を切り、刻む

instructions.en: Stir the chopped jalapeños and shredded cheese into the whisked eggs
instructions.sk: Vmiešajte nasekané jalapeños a nastrúhaný syr do rozšľahaných vajec
instructions.ja: 刻んだハラペーニョとシュレッドチーズを泡立てた卵に混ぜ込む

instructions.en: Pour the mixture into a greased 9x9 inch baking pan
instructions.sk: Nalejte zmes do vymastenej 23x23 cm formy na pečenie
instructions.ja: 混ぜたものを油を塗った23cm四方の焼き皿に注ぐ

instructions.en: Bake at 350°F (175°C) for 15-20 minutes until firm but still slightly soft
instructions.sk: Pečte pri teplote 175°C 15-20 minút, kým nebude pevné, ale stále mierne mäkké
instructions.ja: 350°F（175°C）のオーブンで15〜20分、固まるがまだ少し柔らかい状態になるまで焼く

instructions.en: Cool for 10 minutes before cutting into 1-inch squares
instructions.sk: Pred nakrájaním na 2,5 cm štvorce nechajte 10 minút vychladnúť
instructions.ja: 10分間冷ましてから2.5cm四方に切り分ける

instructions.en: Cut into 36 squares (6 across and 6 down)
